data.description: Owner says SELL family home "Fully Furnished" and turn-key ready to move in in the new year. Just bring your toothbrush to this wonderful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the desirable Avalon neighborhood. This is one of the few homes in Palm Coast with underground utilities and street lighting. Energy efficient Solar Panels for Heating and Cooling are a major money saving feature to this residence. The home features upgraded tile in the kitchen and laminate wood flooring in the living room and bedrooms. The master suite showcases double vanity, shower and separate tub. Outside boasts a covered lanai with Hot Tub (to stay if you would like) and large fenced in backyard. Central Vac system makes upkeep convenient. Other features include security system, sprinkler system, newer HVAC system (2019).    Seller willing to contribute up to $5,000 toward closing costs or interest rate buy down.
